Class SocketClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.controller.SocketClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Observer

    public class SocketClient
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Observer
    This class checks the connection of the player that has chosen "socket mode". After the connection this class receives the data from the server and then calls the methods in the ClientController
